The '''Desert Baretta''', also known as the '''ANKYLO''', is an enemy in ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. It is a hard-hitting enemy encountered in the desert regions of the northern continents. While it drops only one [[gil]], it provides substantial [[experience points]].

